                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On July 10, Lieutenant General Matthew B. Ridgway, Commander in Chief of the
                    United Nations Forces in Korea, met with representatives of the Chinese and
                    North Korean forces in Korea at Kaesong, to begin discussions intended to bring
                    about an armistice. For documentation concerning the talks at Kaesong and the
                    developments leading to their initiation, see <ref target="frus1951v07p1#pg_636"
                        >pages 636</ref> ff.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
